     (b) redistribute the SDK or any of its components as a standalone
         product, library, or service;
     (c) load model files, model identifiers, or latency variants not
         covered by your Rapidly licence, or attempt to bypass, disable,
         or circumvent the licence verification or watermarking
         mechanisms;
     (d) remove, alter, or obscure any copyright, trademark, licence
         notice, or other proprietary marking on the SDK, its model
         files, or any accompanying documentation;
     (e) use the SDK in any manner that violates applicable law or any
         additional terms of your separate commercial agreement.

